---
title: Moroccan Beef Koftas & Garlic Rice with Chermoula Coconut Sauce & Lemony Veggies
description: These koftas are handy parcels of explosive flavour, with tender beef and pork mince, mild spices and a punchy coconut sauce to drizzle over the top. Paired with garlic rice and veggies drizzled with lemon juice, this is a Moroccan-style feast to remember.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-kofta-chermoula-coconut-sauce-f4633b21.jpg
